        <updateDate>2020-03-25T17:51:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Small Business Lending Fairness Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits as a condition to a loan or extension of credit a confession of judgment or similar agreement. (A confession of judgment is an agreement to a judgment of liability without notice and opportunity to be heard in court in the event of the default of a borrower.) </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
